org.universAAL.ucc.model

Class UAPPPart

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.universAAL.ucc.model.UAPPPart

  • public class UAPPPart
extends Object
    An UAPPPart represents a single part of a uapp file. It has a name, an appId, a uapplocation, a version, a description and consists a Part, a bundleId and bundleVersion.
    Author:
    Nicole Merkle
